name: showScreenSet
description: Shows a Gigya screen set. Either locally hosted or hosted in the Gigya console.

params.name: opts
params.description: Options object for showScreenSet function

params.name: opts.screenSet
params.description: Screen set to use. Defaults to {@link GigyaWrapper#screenSet}

params.name: opts.containerID
params.description: DOM id of screen set container. Defaults to {@link GigyaWrapper#containerID}

params.name: opts.startScreen
params.description: The screen to show.

params.name: opts.customLang
params.description: An object which overrules the error message for the selected language.

params.name: opts.onBeforeScreenLoad
params.description: This function is fired on before screen load.

params.name: opts.onAfterScreenLoad
params.description: This function is fired onAfterScreenLoad.

params.name: opts.onAfterSubmit
params.description: This function is fired onAfterSubmit.

params.name: opts.onBeforeSubmit
params.description: This function is fired onBeforeSubmit.

params.name: opts.onFieldChanged
params.description: This function is fired onFieldChanged.

name: hideScreenSet
description: Hides a Gigya screen set. Either locally hosted or hosted in the Gigya console.

params.name: opts
params.description: Options object for showScreenSet function

params.name: opts.screenSet
params.description: Screen set to use. Defaults to {@link GigyaWrapper#screenSet}

params.name: opts.containerID
params.description: DOM id of screen set container. Defaults to {@link GigyaWrapper#containerID}

name: registerEventListeners
description: register to global Gigya events like user login or logout.

params.name: eventListeners
params.description: an object of functions that are fired upon global gigya events.

params.name: opts.onLogin
params.description: This function is fired onLogin.

params.name: opts.onLogout
params.description: This function is fired onLogout.

params.name: opts.onConnectionAdded
params.description: This function is fired onConnectionAdded.

params.name: opts.onConnectionRemoved
params.description: This function is fired onConnectionRemoved.

params.name: opts.onLinkback
params.description: This function is fired onLinkback.

name: getAccountInfo
description: Get Account info for user.

params.name: include
params.description: A comma-separated list of fields to include in the response.

return.description: Resolves an object with errorCode, errorMessage and user account info based on the include parameter.

name: checkLoggedInStatus
description: Check if a user is logged in

return.description: Resolves an object with errorCode, errorMessage and loggedIn true or false.

name: share
description: Share to social provider

params.name: opts
params.description: Options object for the share function

params.name: opts.provider
params.description: Which provider to share too. See gigya docs for possible providers.

params.name: opts.url
params.description: URL to share

params.name: opts.title
params.description: Share title

params.name: opts.subtitle
params.description: Subtitle for share (facebook only)

params.name: opts.description
params.description: Share description

params.name: opts.imageurl
params.description: Image to share

params.name: opts.actionAttributes
params.description: actionAttributes contain a JSON object comprised of a series of attribute keys (categories) with associated values. You can also use a generic "tags" key.

params.name: opts.popupHeight
params.description: popup height

params.name: opts.popupWidth
params.description: popup width

params.name: opts.providerKey
params.description: The provider-specific API Key. This parameter is used when calling this method for providers that require an API key.

params.name: opts.shortURLs
params.description: Using this parameter you may determine whether to use Gigya's URL shortening service for URLs passed in the status parameter. Options: 'never', 'always', 'whenRequired'.

params.name: opts.facebookDialogType
params.description: Applicable only for sharing through Facebook. This parameter determines which Facebook dialog will appear when clicking the share button.

params.name: opts.tags
params.description: A comma separated list of tags that are used to identify the share operation.

name: getSchema
description: Get the userSchema for the current {@link GigyaWrapper#apiKey}

return.description: Resolves an object with errorCode, errorMessage and the schema info.

name: getPolicies
description: Get the Policies from the RaaS console interface

params.name: opts
params.description: Options object for the share function

params.name: opts.sections
params.description: A comma-separated list specifying which sections of the policies to include in the response

return.description: Resolves an object with errorCode, errorMessage and the policies info.

name: getScreenSets
description: Get the Screensets from the RaaS console interface

params.name: opts
params.description: Options object for the share function

params.name: opts.screenSetIDs
params.description: Either a comma separated list or a JSON array of identifiers of the screen-sets to be retrieved.

params.name: opts.include
params.description: A comma separated list of top level fields to include in the response. The default is: "screenSetID,html,css".

return.description: Resolves an object with errorCode, errorMessage and the policies info.

name: _cb
description: Private callback function for the promises used in this class.

params.name: resolve
params.description: Function to fire as resolve.

params.name: reject
params.description: Function to fire as reject.

params.name: response
params.description: Teh response to use for either resolve or reject.

return.description: Resolves or rejects a response object.
